def my_func(input1:str, input2:str):
    if not (1 <= len(input1) <= 20 and 1 <= len(input2) <= 20):
        return []
    result = []
    i = input1.find(input2)
    while i != -1:
        result.append(i)
        i = input1.find(input2, i + 1)
    return result
